Hey all! 

Please consider helping us reach an end of the year goal to raise funds for Feeding Nashville — Feed The Future Fundraiser campaign. 

Since the Spring of 2020 and in conjunction with the Placemat Team, Feeding Nashville has fed over 140,000 meals and developed 30 Community Partner relationships to successfully provide FREE healthy meals to those in need within the Nashville community; at-risk students, families in need, individuals experiencing homelessness, and those recovering from medical procedures.

With your thoughtful support all funds raised will directly impact the greater community of Nashville. Every contribution will continue to help us provide freshly-made, feel-good nutritious meals that are all free of the BIG 8 allergens!

Please help us share and spread the word to your friends, families and community networks. You can find the fundraising link attached in Placemat’s bio above. We wouldn't be able to continue to support our Community Partners and the folks in need with Feeding Nashville meals without your kind generosity. Every dollar raised is greatly appreciated, thank you!

Many thanks to you all! Have a safe holiday season. 

The Placemat Team

I got to spend an afternoon a few years back with Mr. Crosby. He was so warm and friendly to me. We had an incredible long conversation about music, life and family. He invited to come hang out with him at his home sometime, and I was on cloud 9!

I’ll always remember that day as a highlight in my career and life, and will always regret not getting the chance to take him up on his invitation.

The music was mesmerizing, innovative and magical. It will live forever.

Our condolences to his family and friends…. God bless y'all

It’s been hard to keep this one a secret for so long! Storytelling has always been one of my biggest passions and  I’m ready to take that same passion and apply it to something even bigger. I can’t reveal too much just yet, but I can promise you that this company is going to be something special. We’re going to be shaking things up, breaking new ground, and bringing people together in a whole new way. and after years of work behind the scenes, I am beyond thrilled to officially announce the launch of Down Home, a new media production company with @skydance, @shareability, and @emco615.

Follow @downhome to be the first to hear about our upcoming TV and film projects, new content initiatives for fans, artists, and brands, and the growth of our Nashville studios. Can’t wait to unravel the incredible, untold stories with such a talented team!

Just released a new acoustic video for “Remember Me Well” on YouTube. I’ve loved taking some time to strip down these songs before we release the full album next Friday!! Can’t wait!

After everything that happened in the world over the past few years…. it made me want to find and record more meaningful, life affirming songs. This album came out of it, and I truly think it’s the best project we’ve ever made (I feel like I say that every time, but as an artist, I want to work to get better with every record and I’m really proud of this one).
